in this directory, input:

$ ./gc.exe ./a-step50.exe 000 085 8
$ ./gc.exe ./a-step90.exe 000 085 8
$ ./gc.exe ./a-step210.exe 000 085 8

(usage: ./gc.exe step-name start-num end-num processor-num
 if your PC is 4 core 8 thread ,processor-num is 8 )

will create .bat files,copy these files to work_dir and run .

how to show prograss:

input $./moniter

(ps -ef|grep a-step)
